      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut </strong>finely</p>",
