    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Slice 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> into rounds and finely chop the remainder</p><p>Tip: Not a fan of spice? Remove the seeds!</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1687534483132-x200.jpg",
