            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped coriander</strong> to a<strong> </strong>small<strong> </strong>bowl with the <strong>finely chopped green chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lime</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>,<strong> sugar </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> coriander salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1687534487872-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
