        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 4-5 min, remove the tray from the oven and carefully add the<strong> flaked almonds </strong>to the other side of the baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>to the oven for a final 3-4 min or until the almonds are toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 7,
